            <p class="- topic/p ">
               <note class="- topic/note ">The bypass mains needs to be available
and within tolerance. The static switch EN needs to be available.
The switch over do not interrupt the load.</note>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Switch to bypass operation:</p>
                     <ol conref="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/Switch-to-bypass"
                         class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li "/>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Confirm any alarms by pressing the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">C key</b> twice.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure the system operates correctly and no alarms are present.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>The system is in bypass operation and load is supplied by the
bypass mains via the static switch EN.</p>
